text: Nu ("Watery One") or Nun ("The Inert One") is a deity in Ancient Egyptian religion. It looks like a human but represents the cosmic ocean which existed at the time of creation. Nu can be seen as the first of all the gods and the creator of reality. He can also destroy existence and return everything to how it was. Nu's partner was the goddess Nunet.
